snippet.title: Acquiescence - A Dark Surreal Action Platformer
snippet.description: Acquiescence is a Lovecraftian 2D shooting platformer, set within a dark and sombre world filled with blasphemous forces of evil. Can you escape this madness? Is this a dream or a doomed reality? Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1589520/Acquiescence/
